COMMENT ON COLUMN workouts.incline_percent IS '경사도 (%, 트레드밀/러닝)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN workouts.resistance_level IS '저항 레벨 (사이클/로잉 등)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN workouts.primary_metric_value IS '종목별 대표 값 (볼륨, 거리 등)';
